# Create react app using create app

    -goto terminal type the following commaand
        - cd Deskto
        - npx create-react-app (nam eof app should be in small letter no capital letter) movie-gpt
          terminal will stall everything
    -goto tailwind.css go to get started and go framework and select create react app
        - npm install -D tailwindcss
        - npx tailwindcss init
        follow the remaining steps

