# Authentication

    - Need backend(we will we using firebase) and it will to Hosting
    - Goto Firebase
        - Click on Get Started
        - CLick on Create Project
        - Fill the detail it needed
        - Tick on enable google analytic
        - Complete the remaining info ...
        - Goto Build
            - Authentication
                - Enable Email/password authentication

        - execute the command 1 by one
        - npm install firebase
        - npm install -g firebase-tools
    - ecexute (firebase login) command if already login it will show the email else it will ask (y/n) type n enter it will takeU to login
    - Execute firebase login now it will show the login email
    - Execete (firebase init) command for configuration
        - Choose Hoisting: Configure files for firebase Hoisting and .......... click using spacebar for selection and then enter
        - Choose use an existing project hit enter
            - Choose the project who are on firebase currently
                - 1st query ans is (build) 2nd (n) 3rd(n)
    - Done

    # App Deployment
    - npm run build (to build the app)
    - firebase deploy
